1. About

 AModules3 library is aimed to help development of administration systems,
 web pages, web portals, web systems and other web applications. It provides
 a flexible and extendable framework to simplify application development and
 maintenance.

2. What's new in AModules3

 Version 3 brings complete rewrite of the library and now targets much wider
 range of web applications. Major new improvements include:
  - Template support through SMlite
  - Flexible and modular API system
  - PHP5+ (using exceptions and other new features)
  - AJAX support, many other improvements

